sugestao:
1. Crie o script:

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# scripts/install-assets.sh

ASSET_URL="https://kenney.nl/assets/puzzle-pack"
ASSET_ZIP="puzzle-pack.zip"
ASSET_DIR="public/assets"

mkdir -p "$ASSET_DIR"
curl -L -o "$ASSET_ZIP" "https://kenney.nl/assets/download/puzzle-pack.zip"
unzip -o "$ASSET_ZIP" -d "$ASSET_DIR"
rm "$ASSET_ZIP"
```

2. Atualize `public/sw.js` para incluir imagens no cache:

```js
// public/sw.js (trecho)
cache.addAll([
  ...
  '/assets/tile_blue.png',
  '/assets/paddle.png',
  '/assets/ballGrey.png'
]);
```

3. Modifique o `Ball.ts` e `Paddle.ts` para usar `Image()`:

```ts
// src/logic/Ball.ts
const img = new Image();
img.src = "/assets/ballGrey.png";
ctx.drawImage(img, this.x - 8, this.y - 8, 16, 16);
```

```ts
// src/logic/Paddle.ts
const img = new Image();
img.src = "/assets/paddle.png";
ctx.drawImage(img, this.x, 300, this.width, this.height);
```
